OL,7,FWrongfully dismissed for the historic
OL,8,F'crime' of being LGBT and trying to
OL,9,Fserve their country, mistreated
OL,10,Fveterans have, on Thursday, expressed
OL,11,Fanger at the pace of a compensation
OL,12,Fscheme aimed at addressing this
OL,13,Finjustice.
OL,15,FIn December, the government announced
OL,16,Fup to #75 million for the LGBT
OL,17,Ffinancial recognition scheme, with
OL,18,Fpayments of up to #70,000 for each
OL,19,Fveteran "to acknowledge the historic
OL,20,Fwrongs they experienced in the armed
OL,21,Fforces".
