OL,7,FOn Thursday, these same veterans
OL,8,Fexpressed anger and disappointment
OL,9,Fthat out of more than 1,000
OL,10,Fapplications for compensation over the
OL,11,Flast five months - so far just 24 have
OL,12,Fbeen paid.
OL,14,FIf applications were to continue being
OL,15,Fprocessed at this speed it would take
OL,16,Fmore than 17 years to complete the
OL,17,Fcompensation scheme.
