OL,7,FThe Fighting with Pride military
OL,8,Fcharity said eight of the 24 payouts
OL,9,Fwere to veterans with life-limiting
OL,10,Fhealth conditions.
OL,12,FThe charity's chief executive Peter
OL,13,FGibson said older veterans have been
OL,14,Fleft "furious" and feeling that
OL,15,F"justice delayed is justice denied".
