OL,7,FHe has written to Defence Secretary
OL,8,FJohn Healey to convey the "growing
OL,9,Fanger, frustration and impatience" of
OL,10,Fveterans, and to say the scheme "is
OL,11,Fsadly not delivering at a pace which
OL,12,Fmeets the expectations of the ageing
OL,13,Fveterans we are working with".
OL,15,FMr Gibson said a staff of 15 people to
OL,16,Fdeal with the scheme "together with
OL,17,Funderperforming technology is clearly
OL,18,Fand simply not enough to meet the
OL,19,Fdemand".
