OL,7,FEmma Storey, who was under
OL,8,Finvestigation by military police and
OL,9,Fleft the Women's Royal Army Corps in
OL,10,F1987, shared her anger over the delays.
OL,12,FShe said: "We feel angry and
OL,13,Fdisappointed. We were treated
OL,14,Fabysmally during our service. Forced
OL,15,Fout for our sexuality and loving the
OL,16,Fpeople we love, only to be let down by
OL,17,Fa casual approach to the payments
OL,18,Fwe're owed.
