OL,7,FFor many veterans, who are now in
OL,8,Ftheir 60s, 70s, and 80s time is of the
OL,9,Fessence.
OL,11,F"For many it means justice delayed is
OL,12,Fjustice denied. Fighting With Pride
OL,13,Fwill continue to do everything we can
OL,14,Fto find every single affected LGBT
OL,15,Fveteran and ensure they get the
OL,16,Freparations they deserve," said Peter
OL,17,FGibson.
