OL,7,FA Ministry of Defence spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "We recognise the need to work
OL,9,Fquickly through the over 1,000
OL,10,Fapplications for financial recognition
OL,11,Fwe've received.
OL,13,F"The process of working through the
OL,14,Fapplications requires checking a
OL,15,Fnumber of information sources and
OL,16,Fhistorical records, however we
OL,17,Funderstand the need for timeliness in
OL,18,Fdelivering this important scheme.
